column5: *Dynamic Inventory* - INQUIRE FIRST-  *There maybe a cleaning fee of $100 if the booking request is for 5 days or less.*  Three Bedroom: King in master, two full beds in second bedroom, king in third bedroom, sleeper sofa in living area. Maximum occupancy is 10.  High season rates are higher than whats listed on the calendar; Weekends : $360/night Weekday : $300/night  The current rate on the calendar will be valid if the booking request is within 5 days of arrival.
